SUMMARY:Staged Readings
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260809T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260809T190000
DTSTAMP:20260709T151917Z
UID:occ-1764@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Staged Reading
DESCRIPTION:Actors read never-before-produced scripts by local playwrights
  — book in hand\, staging kept minimal.\n\nNew scripts by local playwrig
 hts\, none of them ever produced\, read aloud by actors with book in hand 
 and little more than a sketch of staging. The words carry the whole show\,
  and the audience gets first crack at them. Presented by Merely Players.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260709T063637Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
