BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Support Local Theatre
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261030T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261030T213000
DTSTAMP:20260709T151917Z
UID:occ-1697@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:A costumed murder-mystery party raising money for Merely Playe
 rs\, with clues unfolding all night.\n\nMerely Players' fundraiser takes t
 he shape of an interactive whodunit: guests arrive in costume and masks\, 
 clues surface as the night goes on\, and anyone in the room can crack the 
 case. Dogwood Social pours specialty cocktails\, and a 50/50 raffle and si
 lent auction round out the fundraising. Masks are sold on site for anyone 
 who wants to add to the intrigue.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260709T063637Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/shakesbeer-1-2
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Other Desert Cities
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261106T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261106T213000
DTSTAMP:20260709T151917Z
UID:occ-1701@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Jon Robin Baitz's Pulitzer-finalist family drama: a daughter's
  tell-all memoir detonates a Palm Springs Christmas.\n\nJon Robin Baitz's 
 drama\, a finalist for the 2012 Pulitzer Prize\, unfolds over Christmas Ev
 e 2004 in Palm Springs. Brooke Wyeth comes home after six years away with 
 a finished memoir that digs into the death of her brother\, a chapter her 
 staunchly Republican parents have spent decades keeping closed. Her aunt S
 ilda\, fresh from rehab and firmly on the other side of the political fenc
 e\, is also in the house. The festive reunion turns into a fight over memo
 ry\, loyalty\, and who gets to tell the family's story. Presented by Merel
 y Players.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260709T063637Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/other-desert-citie
 s-11-06-26
END:VEVENT
