SUMMARY:Support Local Theatre
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270313T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270313T213000
DTSTAMP:20260709T151917Z
UID:occ-1698@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:A costumed murder-mystery party raising money for Merely Playe
 rs\, with clues unfolding all night.\n\nMerely Players' fundraiser takes t
 he shape of an interactive whodunit: guests arrive in costume and masks\, 
 clues surface as the night goes on\, and anyone in the room can crack the 
 case. Dogwood Social pours specialty cocktails\, and a 50/50 raffle and si
 lent auction round out the fundraising. Masks are sold on site for anyone 
 who wants to add to the intrigue.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260709T063637Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/a-celtic-celebrati
 on-featuring-the-bordercollies
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Clean House
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270409T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270409T213000
DTSTAMP:20260709T151917Z
UID:occ-1704@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:Sarah Ruhl's whimsical comedy about a Brazilian housekeeper wh
 o'd rather craft the perfect joke than clean.\n\nSarah Ruhl's play\, a 200
 5 Pulitzer finalist\, starts with a mess: Lane\, a doctor\, has hired Mati
 lde\, a housekeeper who dreams of being a comedian and refuses to clean. L
 ane's sister Virginia\, who finds cleaning a calling\, secretly takes over
  the housework\, and the discoveries in the laundry pull the whole househo
 ld somewhere stranger and sadder. Variety praised its "screwy poetry and p
 enetrating wisdom." Presented by Merely Players.
GEO:33.9031178;-84.2776526
LAST-MODIFIED:20260709T063637Z
LOCATION:Merely Players Presents\, 3785 King Ave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.merelyplayerspresents.com/event-details/the-clean-house-04
 -09-27
END:VEVENT
